'''Kayson's Weapons Shop''' was based in [[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]] and was a distributor of firearms. It was probably the best weapons shop in the [[City/Legends|city]] and was run by [[Kayson]], a grizzled [[Alien/Legends|alien]], who was also very adept at obtaining weapons on the black market. He sold a variety of legal weapons, all in excellent condition, but also offered contraband to trusted customers.<ref name="GG1" />

